mami Puppy Love Moment With Lookmhee-Sonya
Saturday, November 2, 2024 (from 03:00 AM to 06:00 PM)
Mami invites fans of "Lookmhee-Sonya," the two stunningly hot actresses from the series Affair: Love Games, to join the event "mami Puppy Love Moment With Lookmhee-Sonya." This exclusive activity will allow the fans to experience the sweet and adorable moments with both actresses, along with the opportunity to try out products that will enhance your lips' beauty all day long, such as mami Puppy Love Tint, a long-lasting, beautifully pigmented lip tint.
